<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    Hi <%= @brother.first_name %>, 
    <br>
    <% if @debts.count > 1 %>
        My records show that you have the following overdue debts to the house: 
        <ul>
        	<% @debts.each do |debt| %>
        		<li> <%= number_to_currency debt.amount %> for <%= debt.name %>, due <%= time_ago_in_words(debt.due) %> ago</li>
        	<% end %>
        	<br>
        	<b>Total: <%= number_to_currency @total %> </b>
        </ul>
    <% else %>
        My records show that you still owe <%= number_to_currency @debts.first.amount %> for <%= @debts.first.name %>, which was due <%= time_ago_in_words(@debts.first.due) %> ago.
    <% end %>
    Make a check to 'Phi Gamma Delta' as soon as possible. If you have any questions, please reply to this email or contact me directly. 
    <br>
    <br>
    Best, 
    <br>
    Will
  </body>
</html>
